    Your privacy is important to us, and we are here to address any concerns you may have.
    <br><br>
    By using MK Scholars' services, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms and conditions. We are committed to providing a secure and supportive environment for students to access scholarships and academic resources globally while respecting your privacy and data rights.
